    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * Hamsters</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Hamster_in_hand-cropped.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/Hamster_in_hand-cropped.jpg/330px-Hamster_in_hand-cropped.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"241\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/Hamster_in_hand-cropped.jpg/500px-Hamster_in_hand-cropped.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/0b/Hamster_in_hand-cropped.jpg/960px-Hamster_in_hand-cropped.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Hamster_in_hand-cropped.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Hamster Egbert <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Hamsters</b>,<br />\nan <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant multi-hamster chess engine by <a href=\"/Alessandro_Scotti\" title=\"Alessandro Scotti\">Alessandro Scotti</a> with the goal of a program that has a full-featured and correct implementation of the UCI protocol, and that is able to play standard chess as well as <a href=\"/Chess960\" title=\"Chess960\">Chess960</a>. \nIt applies a <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">parallel search</a> utilizing up to 8 <a href=\"/Thread\" title=\"Thread\">threads</a>. Binaries are available for <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a> and <a href=\"/Mac_OS\" title=\"Mac OS\">Mac OS X</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. Hamsters played the <a href=\"/CIPS_2007\" title=\"CIPS 2007\">CIPS 2007</a>, and was runner-up behind <a href=\"/Delfi\" title=\"Delfi\">Delfi</a> at the <a href=\"/CCC_2008\" title=\"CCC 2008\">CCC 2008</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Games\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Games</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2007\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2007</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2008\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2008</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Games\">Selected Games</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hamsters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Games\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><a href=\"/CCC_2008\" title=\"CCC 2008\">CCC 2008</a>, round 3, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Hamsters</a> -  <a href=\"/Chiron\" title=\"Chiron\">Chiron</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<pre>\n[Event \"Chess Computer Cup 2008\"]\n[Site \"Turin\"]\n[Date \"2008.12.06\"]\n[Round \"3\"]\n[White \"Hamsters, 0.7.1.\"]\n[Black \"Chiron, v0.8.7\"]\n[Result \"1-0\"]\n\n1.d4 Nf6 2.Nf3 g6 3.c4 Bg7 4.Nc3 d5 5.Qb3 dxc4 6.Qxc4 O-O 7.e4 a6 8.Qb3 b5 \n9.e5 Nfd7 10.e6 fxe6 11.Qxe6+ Kh8 12.Qe4 Nb6 13.Qh4 Nc6 14.Bd3 Bf5 15.Ng5 h5 \n16.Bxf5 Rxf5 17.Be3 Bxd4 18.g4 Bxc3+ 19.bxc3 Qd5 20.O-O Qc4 21.f4 Rf6 22.gxh5 \nKg7 23.hxg6 Rh8 24.Qg3 Nd5 25.Rae1 e6 26.Bc1 Nd8 27.Rf2 Qxc3 28.Rg2 Qxg3 \n29.Rxg3 Rh6 30.Bb2 Rhxg6 31.Nxe6+ Nxe6 32.Bxf6+ Kxf6 33.Rxg6+ Kxg6 34.Rxe6+ \nKf7 35.Rc6 b4 36.Rxa6 Ke7 37.f5 Nb6 38.Ra5 Nd7 39.h4 Nf6 40.Ra6 Nh5 41.Kf2 \nKd7 42.Kf3 c6 43.Kg4 Nf6+ 44.Kg5 Ne4+ 45.Kg6 Nc5 46.Ra7+ Kd6 47.h5 b3 48.axb3 \nNd3 49.h6 Kc5 50.h7 Nf4+ 51.Kg5 Nh3+ 52.Kh4 Nf4 53.h8=Q Nd5 54.Ra4 Kd6 55.Qb8+\nKe7 56.Qe5+ Kf7 57.Ra7+ Nc7 58.Rxc7+ Kf8 59.Qh8# 1-0\n</pre>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hamsters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Gerbil\" title=\"Gerbil\">Gerbil</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Kiwi\" title=\"Kiwi\">Kiwi</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Rodent\" title=\"Rodent\">Rodent</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Sungorus\" title=\"Sungorus\">Sungorus</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hamsters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2007\">2007</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hamsters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2007\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=13490\">Hamsters 0.3 beta 3: HUMAN testers needed!</a> by <a href=\"/Alessandro_Scotti\" title=\"Alessandro Scotti\">Alessandro Scotti</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 30, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=13632\">Hamsters 0.3&#160;: 2418</a> by <a href=\"/Patrick_Buchmann\" title=\"Patrick Buchmann\">Patrick Buchmann</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 08, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=14239\">Hamsters randomizer in action</a> by <a href=\"/Alessandro_Scotti\" title=\"Alessandro Scotti\">Alessandro Scotti</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 03, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=15540\">An interesting bug in Hamsters</a> by <a href=\"/Alessandro_Scotti\" title=\"Alessandro Scotti\">Alessandro Scotti</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 02, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Pawn_Hash_Table\" title=\"Pawn Hash Table\">Pawn Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=15597\">Hamsters 0.4 is out</a> by <a href=\"/Alessandro_Scotti\" title=\"Alessandro Scotti\">Alessandro Scotti</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 05, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=16131\">Hamsters CCRL rating</a> by <a href=\"/Uri_Blass\" title=\"Uri Blass\">Uri Blass</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 30, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=16535\">Hamsters 0.5 released</a> by <a href=\"/Alessandro_Scotti\" title=\"Alessandro Scotti\">Alessandro Scotti</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 18, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=16550\">Hamsters 0.5&#160;: 2450</a> by <a href=\"/Patrick_Buchmann\" title=\"Patrick Buchmann\">Patrick Buchmann</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 19, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=18256\">Hamsters 0.6 released</a> by <a href=\"/Alessandro_Scotti\" title=\"Alessandro Scotti\">Alessandro Scotti</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 07, 2007</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=18345\">LMR: history or not?</a> by <a href=\"/Alessandro_Scotti\" title=\"Alessandro Scotti\">Alessandro Scotti</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 13, 2007&#160;» <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2008\">2008</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hamsters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2008\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=19206\">Hamsters 0.6 - 2665 in CCRL 40/4 blitz</a> by <a href=\"/Kirill_Kryukov\" title=\"Kirill Kryukov\">Kirill Kryukov</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 26, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=23686\">Hamsters 0.7 released</a> by <a href=\"/Alessandro_Scotti\" title=\"Alessandro Scotti\">Alessandro Scotti</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 12, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=23713\">Hamsters 0.7&#160;: 2507</a> by <a href=\"/Patrick_Buchmann\" title=\"Patrick Buchmann\">Patrick Buchmann</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 14, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=24757\">Hamsters 0.7.1 released</a> by <a href=\"/Alessandro_Scotti\" title=\"Alessandro Scotti\">Alessandro Scotti</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 06, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=24781\">Hamsters 0.7.1&#160;: 2510</a> by <a href=\"/Patrick_Buchmann\" title=\"Patrick Buchmann\">Patrick Buchmann</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 08, 2008</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hamsters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Engine\">Chess Engine</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hamsters&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Engine\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://walkofmind.com/programming/chess/hamsters.htm\">Hamsters Homepage</a> by <a href=\"/Alessandro_Scotti\" title=\"Alessandro Scotti\">Alessandro Scotti</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://walkofmind.com/programming/chess/hamsters_story_1.htm\">Hamsters - The story (part 1)</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"